room_title: Escape room "Skull & Bones" by Escape Zone Long Island in New York
room_address: 872 Middle Country Rd. Saint James, NY 11780
room_description: Ahoy Captain! Your crew is ready for the final looting! Remember, the pirates you are robbing are clever and conniving. It will take more than bravery to secure this treasure. It will take brains as well. Get on and off their ship in less than one hour or all that will remain will be your Skull & Bones!
